pical moist [[montane forest]]s.\nIt is threatened by [[habitat loss]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q1269494}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:greytail, equatorial}}\n[[Category:Xenerpestes|equatorial greytail]]\n[[Category:Birds of the Ecuadorian Andes]]\n[[Category:Birds of the Peruvian Andes]]\n[[Category:Birds described in 1885|equatorial greytail]]\n[[Category:Taxa named by W\u0142adys\u0142aw Taczanowski|equatorial greytail]]\n[[Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Furnariidae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Equatorial_greytail"}
